latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Stay at Vedic Village and experience the Durga Puja celebration in a grand way. Celebrate in a traditional Bengali Pujo ambience amidst the abundant greenery of nature. latestIgtvVideos.title: Durga Pujo Stories 2019
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Stay at Vedic Village Spa Resort and experience the 13th Durga Puja celebration in a grand way. Enjoy with your family in a traditional Bengali Pujo ambience with an array of festive activities for everyone. From anjali, aarti, dhunuchi naach competition, phuchka-eating competition, sit & draw for kids, your Pujo at Vedic Village Spa Resort is going to be a memorable and one-of-a-kind experience. Indulge in delectable Bengali delicacies, the ingredients of which are fresh and handpicked for the most authentic experience. Let the celebrations begin!

#VedicVillageSpaResort #VedicPujo

latestPosts.caption:
Rajib Roy Choudhury has been elevated to Associate Vice President at Vedic Village Spa Resort

Rajib Roy Choudhury has been promoted to Associate Vice President at Vedic Village Spa Resort — a pioneering sustainable destination nestled in the Gangetic Plains, conveniently located near Kolkata International Airport and the city’s Central Business District.

Following a successful four-year stint as Senior General Manager, Rajib will now lead overall brand and operational alignment, while spearheading multiple sustainable development initiatives across the group. His deep expertise will play a key role in driving operational excellence, ensuring brand consistency, and advancing innovative eco-friendly practices. This move further strengthens Vedic Village’s position as a leader in sustainable hospitality and supports the group’s long-term vision of growth and environmental responsibility.

@choudhuryrajib, @vedicvillagesparesort
